in/promotion.py`\n- **Profile definitions:** `C:/cursor/tapps_brain/src/tapps_brain/profile.py`\n- **Built-in YAML profiles:** `C:/cursor/tapps-brain/src/tapps_brain/profiles/*.yaml` (6 files)\n- **Store integration:** `C:/cursor/tapps-brain/src/tapps_brain/store.py` (lines 155, 204-224, 676-707)\n- **Tests:** `C:/cursor/tapps-brain/tests/unit/test_promotion.py` (392 lines of comprehensive tests)\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Key Features**\n\n- **Demotion support:** Each layer can define `demotion_to` (separate from promotion), checked by `PromotionEngine.check_demotion()` \n- **Desirable difficulty bonus:** Reinforcement boost scales by `(1.0 - decayed_confidence)` (promotion.py, lines 134-149)\n- **Effective half-life growth:** Memories grow longer half-lives with reinforcement via `log1p(reinforce_count) * 0.3` multiplier (Jost's First Law)\n- **Profile inheritance:** Profiles can extend parent profiles via `extends` field"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a97890648870b7c16 (use SendMessage with to: 'a97890648870b7c16' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 69097\ntool_uses: 31\nduration_ms: 56248</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b61393de-68e8-4cff-8475-056605bcfefe","uuid":"9d96cf9a-14b1-4332-8bb1-c2ce94a3c8f8","timestamp":"2026-03-22T22:34:47.081Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Search thoroughly in C:\\cursor\\tapps-brain for:\n\n1. PromotionConfig or promotion configuration classes/dataclasses\n2. Default promotion thresholds (access counts, time periods)\n3. How promotion is enabled/disabled per profile\n4. The promotion module structure and key functions\n\nLook in src/tapps_brain/promotion/, src/tapps_brain/profile/, and any config files.\nReturn file paths, line numbers, and relevant code snippets showing the promotion threshold configuration.","agentId":"a97890648870b7c16","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have all the information. Let me compile a comprehensive report with file paths and code snippet